2=26-2\cdot12
\begin{align*} 2&=26-2\cdot12\\ &=26-2(38-26)\\ &=3\cdot26-2\cdot38\\ &=3(64-38)-2\cdot38\\ &=3\cdot64-5\cdot38\\ &=3\cdot64-5(102-64)\\ &=8\cdot64-5\cdot102 \end{align*}
\gcd(102,64)=2
-5\times102+8\times64=2
